---
title: Oven-Baked Spiced Basa on Harissa Risotto with Charred Courgette and Cheese
description: Love risottos, but wish there was no stirring involved? This Oven-Baked Spiced Basa on Harissa Risotto is a simplified version of the traditional risotto, baking in the oven instead to absorb all the stock and flavours.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R47_W38_UK_R20089-3_Main_F1_low_2-b83d8dd9.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/66969a06be78f55290ac0873-en-GB.pdf
servings: 2
source: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipes/oven-baked-spiced-basa-on-harissa-risotto-66969a06be78f55290ac0873
author: Anushka Magan
course: main course
cuisine: Middle Eastern
time required: 45 minutes
nutrition:
  calories: 784 kcal
  fat: 23.2 g
